hopobject.body: Where did you go to university? healthpronetwork.com Schioppo, who is 5-foot-10 and weighs approximately 165 pounds, said he couldn’t break the rear side window, so he decided to punch through the back window instead. With water about five feet deep up to his neck, he was “then able to climb in partially and grab him and pull him out onto the trunk. Then I handed him off to Dan and Josh and they pulled him onto the dock. Twenty seconds later, the car completely sank into the water.”
